{"tid":2253106,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"3.3億港元票房《鬼滅之刃》加持 LiSA破宇多田光16年來記錄","createTime":"2020-10-22T02:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T04:58:38.000Z","uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea7d0c43f4a73c47f5eb2d948ae92d64ab30638","tid":2253106,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T02:51:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/648p405/0x0/100/hd/c4aee13be92b826e8e405a9f68c2aec0/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201021/_2020102120253917242.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F648p405%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Fc4aee13be92b826e8e405a9f68c2aec0%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201021%2F_2020102120253917242.jpeg&h=f3a70e96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLiSA拎住單曲碟《炎》合照。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本漫畫《鬼滅之刃》16年開始連載，動漫版19年在日本播映，上周五更添食首齣電影《鬼滅之刃劇場版無限列車篇》。電影現已大破日本票房紀錄，上映3日大收46億日圓（約3.36億港元），不少戲院場次均告爆滿。而《鬼滅之刃》動漫和電影主題曲的主唱歌手，33歲的LiSA近日亦超有人氣。電影主題曲《炎》在10月12日至18日期間下載量有14.1萬次，是女歌手史上最高記錄。收錄電視主題曲《紅蓮華》的專輯《LEO-NiNE》，亦同時打上大碟榜、數碼大碟榜和綜合大碟榜的銷量冠軍，是繼宇多田光後，相隔16年才再有女歌手創下這佳績。LiSA一星期內在日本Oricon周間音樂排行榜更連奪7個冠軍，《鬼滅之刃》所帶來的強大影響力實在不能輕視。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《鬼滅之刃》掀起一股潮流，日本傳媒報導，有人在網上炒賣《鬼滅》戲飛，甚至連戲院購票所贈送的禮物都以高價出售，令真正《鬼滅》Fans得不到心頭好。電影將於11月12日在港上映，香港《鬼滅》Fans記得唔好亂咁炒周邊呀。"},{"pid":"27d1cc254c1fdfef0d048d6634b50f9578378ea3","tid":2253106,"uid":155374,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:08:25.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">負皮, block, 上一頁</span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">會員 <strong>希特拉 #25345</strong> 係支那狗嚟</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸都整到3A game<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2202894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2202894</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n原神=免費撒爾達,冇switch既可以滿足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2226177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2226177</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n原神：才兩天我就患上這些毛病，實在是不敢玩下去！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2226591\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2226591</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n原神 外媒評分出爐 : 驚艷迷人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2232419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2232419</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n《原神》發佈10天全球收入近9000萬美元，締造二次元新紀錄！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2238115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2238115</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ca67448cb20617854c7287f18ee4ad91debf0b9b","tid":2253106,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"日本啲星 紅極一時 冷靜返人氣之後就會頂唔順自殺"},{"pid":"db7561bc54b671c8ff79d88d7f890af5c4d91c80","tid":2253106,"uid":66379,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ca67448cb20617854c7287f18ee4ad91debf0b9b","tid":2253106,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"日本啲星 紅極一時 冷靜返人氣之後就會頂唔順自殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個又唔係一定嘅 宇多田光都無"},{"pid":"7bc78f1a48d69ae5ed79ece1b3238cd6058ad7cd","tid":2253106,"uid":93620,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca67448cb20617854c7287f18ee4ad91debf0b9b","tid":2253106,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"日本啲星 紅極一時 冷靜返人氣之後就會頂唔順自殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:39:49.000Z","msg":"LiSA 本身唱動漫歌已經好紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6b043778dae275e9fc9ef99d26293985523b55","tid":2253106,"uid":189317,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca67448cb20617854c7287f18ee4ad91debf0b9b","tid":2253106,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"日本啲星 紅極一時 冷靜返人氣之後就會頂唔順自殺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:45:55.000Z","msg":"LiSA本身就紅緊，而且唔係突然紅